description: Includes papers presented at the International Conference on Regional Integration and Institutionalization held at Aoyama Gakuin University, January 22-23, 2011., "This book was published as the fruit of a three-year and five-year research between 2008-2011 and 2008-2013 respectively about the 'The enlarged EU and East Asian regional cooperation in the international politics - integration, security and social security.'"--p. 1.
title: Regional Integration and Institutionalization, Regional Integration and Institutionalization Comparing Asia and Europe
